1
00:00:02,260 --> 00:00:05,560
Before the two of them arrived here, they only had each other.

2
00:00:05,740 --> 00:00:07,720
They were truly alone in this world.

3
00:00:08,540 --> 00:00:12,700
They were found walking hand in hand near the border of Czechoslovakia.

4
00:00:13,440 --> 00:00:17,040
Just the two of them, shivering all alone in the cold.

5
00:00:19,440 --> 00:00:23,760
I heard that the conditions in the orphanages in East Germany were pretty terrible.

6
00:00:23,760 --> 00:00:27,200
Not all orphanages were like 5-1-1 Kinderheim.

7
00:00:39,800 --> 00:00:42,940
Inga, dear, the bathroom is the other way.

8
00:00:43,440 --> 00:00:44,660
Down the hall, okay?

9
00:00:47,960 --> 00:00:48,560
Mommy!

10
00:00:49,720 --> 00:00:51,800
It's all right. It's all right.

11
00:00:53,880 --> 00:00:56,920
Now you can go to the bathroom by yourself, can't you?

12
00:01:04,300 --> 00:01:07,980
These poor children have never really felt the love of a parent.

13
00:01:08,640 --> 00:01:12,160
In order to develop as a person, the only thing you need is love.

14
00:01:12,660 --> 00:01:17,420
The orphanages of the East Side were truly horrible places for the children to grow up in.

15
00:01:17,900 --> 00:01:22,160
Everything was so impersonal. Even this place was only known by the number 47.

16
00:01:23,760 --> 00:01:29,360
We did everything we could do within our power so that we wouldn't be controlled by the government

17
00:01:29,360 --> 00:01:33,080
We weren't going to be another 5-1-1 Kinderheim

18
00:01:34,340 --> 00:01:39,540
It was a special orphanage controlled by the Ministry of Welfare and the Ministry of the Interior

19
00:01:40,080 --> 00:01:41,840
Do you know what that means?

20
00:01:42,620 --> 00:01:47,920
No, the reality was it was the Ministry of the Interior's pet project

21
00:01:47,920 --> 00:01:51,740
East Germany was using that place for experimentation

22
00:01:51,740 --> 00:01:53,840
on the children.

23
00:01:56,160 --> 00:01:57,160
[dramatic music]

24
00:02:03,040 --> 00:02:05,520
